SETUP STEPS:
1. Install Python from python.org
2. Install requests library: pip install requests
3. Install OpenVPN from openvpn.net/community-downloads
4. Get a FREE Los Angeles .ovpn config file from:
   → vpnbook.com (free, pick a US server)
   → protonvpn.com (free tier, pick US-LA)
5. Place the .ovpn file in THIS folder
5. Double-click run.bat AS ADMINISTRATOR

KILL SWITCH:
If VPN drops, all internet is blocked automatically.
Click the button to disconnect and restore internet.
For Direct Kill Switch:
1. netsh advfirewall set allprofiles firewallpolicy blockinbound,allowoutbound
2. taskkill /F /IM openvpn.exe